<event name="START_BEACON_COMPATIBILITY">
	<text>It appears you are playing on a ship not designed for Multiverse! Do you believe this to be incorrect? Please report it so we or the appropriate developers can correct it!
	It is heavily recommended you do not use ships or other mods not made for Multiverse to prevent issues. However, since you are, we have added some markers needed for compatibility. This will prevent some errors, but does not guarantee you won't have issues.
	If you wish to update the ship you are playing to support MV but don't know how, feel free to ask about it on the forums or our discord, we'll be happy to help.</text>
	<hiddenAug>SHIP_MULTIVERSE</hiddenAug>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="START_BEACON_PRESELECT"/>
	</choice>
</event>
